metadata.name: MR. Giraffe JS&ALH
metadata.description:
Giraffe shows confidence and self-esteem. He is proud of his appearance and knows that he is truly unique in the world. Being different is not a negative thing . Because a giraffe is a different animal, I show with this work that being different is not a bad thing. He can do many things. He can be an artist, a doctor, an engineer, a superhero, etc. Many other things.
